oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: J. K. Barlow block
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of the brick building that housed the Dr. J. K. Barlow store. Store signs are placed in the window and several men are standing on the sidewalk.
This is now occupied by Rexall Drugs.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Stores & shops; Streets
